parameters: Why are you here? Did you finish your rehearsal?
你怎么在这里？排练结束了吗？
Other classes have occupied our place temporarily, I decided to working on the script first
暂时把场地让给别的班了，我先把剧本写完
The show will begin tomorrow, you sure you're okey with this?
明天就要演出了，真的没问题吗
I feel like I'm full of inspiration right now!
And indeed writing the story is the first priority
而且确实是应该先把故事想好再去考虑其它事情
我之前的想法确实有点问题
这么说还真是多亏了雅莉同学呢
Can you help me give this candy to Ari?
那你能帮我把这包糖果给雅莉同学吗？
Why don't you give it to her yourself?
那为什么你不自己给她呢
Ugh...Umm...Oh! I need work on scripts!
I can reluctantly accepted this excuse
这个理由我勉强接受吧
Wait! How can I find her!
She is drawing board paints at classroom
她现在在课室画黑板报
Actually that's what I was going to do......
其实我本来也是打算去画黑板报的……
en = Talk to Ari in class 901
